pUfa2Lmea97Jq_4Fxak/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="在特朗普发表伊朗言论之前，期货市场交易量激增"&gt;特朗普在社交媒体上发帖前几分钟&lt;/a&gt;，与至少 600 万桶布伦特原油和西德克萨斯中质原油相关的&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;价值数十亿美元&lt;/strong&gt;的期货和金融合约被售出，引发了要求调查的呼声。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;地缘政治的不确定性&lt;/strong&gt;推动了预测市场活动的激增。对美国和伊朗之间停火的投注已让 Polymarket 流入超过 1.7 亿美元，使其成为该平台短暂历史上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/01_UAqn0NQBnbNwxb3ZfbfWpUfqYTFuPkJlo7dwCI3NMwGc8Y-_c2IG2oKzPpjBm_k2lTSpLd5GWS7BxfB58BsAsE5q9AmX0DAR2mR9HMgGa0hQQt0WBmtPGmtIzRBqT5jWgdfQ5L_1WpJfxEd0-46an1aE77oYHyFqZ_3sHke9v_zIeqt4NUSgBaVfRyZMW4mDqsCZXSVqMLOJcjCPH9fA81U6I7w25WRczXZBq064kNDtFI5k0fk6gPUIY4TnmqfvtEPArnVJjf0mD6BZ_zm4i_manqLpqz-UMEluOXCe7-PlSFCsH6izGUksbA9CGh8GnFdwH_x6QQ3w6L9adfmaLVbg3himH1hONZHup-iDtG9idoOdsV8Yy4GJlZ7BnRv6cUJX-dWAYr5bRLE87vBxPeHzbC5UjoEq4XrdNqaP5qa23psKhVRXJZL3zfRKuvc6wxBuXGfPlZoQxuMjDmtw-o7ZF5_orC_cuR6apmLrl7Zv7YoL_jxlNcbIW23MCZ5abnjpMDgzwEqn4Dk2hZPEii0DGrZtq/841t3rHc9zUY_wET9n0sRxBXpzntlyQp/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="Polymarket 伊朗赌注引发新争议和内部审查"&gt;最大的地缘政治投注之一&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着特朗普政府&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/NDyf1B6E7cKFFgONLCDiYdWdfTFb_CnTujJtv__BlCF1gUk4sp6N1egUBHhvwMV77W5XoGBfqNnFhahvH8i1X4JFU4bhqVnerVR090HuMncYhjH2B6_EkbQzNj8QJMNJd6JQBcmQVka8e-YKrHDUc9A5HMK4HBrsL2-rowILJjY8riIP1KDBFAiCiUgOPrTS-bcDJdBOzFHsCztFqoi9Qe9n5Z6CLxHzbjDDgdeuXb2yYE209qIPB7_A55Yn5BDyzZFU8-v0vgQRMW7mML0CWpNJRou7N4U9oPL5tnhE4RcOwBXaNTxV6dmi8zSMpnRVVIOjTXQvPNvphrKoCh6c7aPCGyDIMgJoZjkggLU6JzY5y-HrTCRhEsBs1Dni1GZaXQAAuHqyDW36-tQQitlxssK7ln-TcarDmGHMLzdSkLq6Ld0itLSKMhWU-m471i82pcbTfcfBYUGw1dcR9fNDte0hiyPvkvJt90vR4-8wC5LEIfW0x6Y2AShfRg1gy8ia6KkrPDJ1YbICW_H6dTthCux2zxf_P84/QkFywhzPbwJ2NG